# Cursor Rules — @dangbt/pro-ui Project

## UI Library
Use @dangbt/pro-ui. Import from package root: `import { Button, ProTable } from '@dangbt/pro-ui'`

## Component Map
- Data table → ProTable (request/dataSource prop)
- Form → ProForm + ProFormInput/Select/etc (Zod schema)
- App shell → Layout
- Modal/dialog → Modal inside DialogTrigger
- Side panel → Drawer inside DialogTrigger
- Notifications → toast.success/error/warning
- KPI metric → Statistic
- Status chip → Badge (success/warning/danger/info)

## Button: use `onPress` not `onClick`. Variants: solid/outline/ghost/danger.

## Colors: use semantic tokens (bg-surface, text-fg, border-border) not bg-white/text-gray-*.

## App root needs: <ThemeProvider><ToastProvider /></ThemeProvider>
